  "response": "As of 2023, the salary for an **Android developer with 4+ years of experience in Dublin, Ireland** typically ranges between **\u20ac50,000 to \u20ac80,000 per year**, depending on factors such as the company, specific skills, and negotiation. \n\nHere\u2019s a more detailed breakdown:\n- **Mid-level range (4\u20136 years experience)**: \u20ac50,000\u2013\u20ac65,000\n- **Senior-level range (6+ years experience or specialized skills)**: \u20ac65,000\u2013\u20ac80,000+\n\nSalaries also vary depending on:\n- The size and industry of the employer (e.g., multinational tech companies may offer higher salaries).\n- Additional skills like Kotlin, Jetpack Compose, or experience with Agile/Scrum methodologies.\n- Benefits such as bonuses, stock options, or health insurance.\n\nFor the most accurate and up-to-date information, platforms like **Glassdoor**, **Payscale**, and **LinkedIn Salary Insights** are great resources.",
